      "span_text": "As shown in Fig. 3B (arrow heads in lane 3), UBE1 was FAT10ylated by the conjugation machinery consisting of UBA6 and USE1 but without the help of an E3 ligase as it is also described for some SUMO substrates where an E3 ligase is not necessarily needed to transfer SUMO onto a substrate [CITATION_1] .",
